                  <dt>Descriptions</dt>
          <dd>
            <dl>
                              <dt>Description</dt>
                <dd>Plain spool form, applied with reeded borders, the flat top with central well flanked by three cast free-standing outwardly curving scrolls with flared bases, the base engraved G over IE, the side under the rim later engraved (upside down): The Gift of Mr. Richard Harris of Cambridge. 1644</dd>
                                                       </dl>
          </dd>
        
